1
00:00:00,505 --> 00:00:08,605
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,780 --> 00:00:17,017
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,255 --> 00:00:19,246
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,260 --> 00:00:26,026
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,097 --> 00:00:29,464
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,667 --> 00:00:33,228
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,605 --> 00:00:36,972
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,041 --> 00:00:44,470
<i>Dreaming of only"the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,549 --> 00:00:53,685
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,758 --> 00:01:01,790
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:02,033 --> 00:01:08,871
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,940 --> 00:01:17,006
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,315 --> 00:01:25,780
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,857 --> 00:01:27,882
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:35,010 --> 00:01:38,776
Sasuke's movements have stopped!
There's still quite a bit of distance, though...

16
00:01:41,016 --> 00:01:43,382
<i>So Sasuke caught up to him, huh?</i>

17
00:01:44,386 --> 00:01:45,216
<i>Okay!</i>

18
00:01:45,688 --> 00:01:47,849
Huh? This smell is?!

19
00:01:50,226 --> 00:01:52,353
W-What's wrong?!

20
00:01:52,828 --> 00:01:54,557
Did something happen to Sasuke?!

21
00:01:55,798 --> 00:01:57,766
I didn't notice until now.

22
00:01:59,101 --> 00:02:00,193
You...

23
00:02:00,970 --> 00:02:03,495
use the same shampoo as me.

24
00:02:06,809 --> 00:02:10,939
This floral green fragrance...
No doubt!

25
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,980
H-Hey now!

26
00:02:13,382 --> 00:02:16,715
Well... my coat's shinier.

27
00:02:16,786 --> 00:02:20,381
Don't be saying stupid things
at such an important time!

28
00:02:20,623 --> 00:02:22,784
- I'm the same as a dog?
- Sorry, sorry...

29
00:02:23,626 --> 00:02:26,356
Same as a dog... Same as a dog...

30
00:02:26,529 --> 00:02:28,497
- Hey Sakura?
- Same as a dog...

31
00:02:28,998 --> 00:02:30,192
Same as a dog...

32
00:02:31,167 --> 00:02:34,159
Same as a dog... Same as a dog...

33
00:02:34,937 --> 00:02:37,633
Hey Sakura...!
Wait!

34
00:02:37,973 --> 00:02:40,806
Oh! Hey! Don't go ahead of me!

35
00:02:41,510 --> 00:02:46,470
<i>A Mistake from the Past.</i>
<i>A Face Revealed!</i>

36
00:02:49,552 --> 00:02:50,314
Dang it!

37
00:02:51,854 --> 00:02:53,788
Sasuke Uchiha!

38
00:02:56,091 --> 00:02:58,059
I won't let you get away now!

39
00:02:59,962 --> 00:03:03,955
<i>Jeez, this kid of all people...</i>
<i>at a time when Gaara is like this.</i>

40
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:06,229
<i>Man, this is bad.</i>

41
00:03:09,605 --> 00:03:11,368
Heh! That's fine.

42
00:03:12,942 --> 00:03:15,308
Kankuro! Take Gaara and go quickly!

43
00:03:20,382 --> 00:03:21,872
Leave him to me!

44
00:03:23,219 --> 00:03:24,550
But Temari...!

45
00:03:25,087 --> 00:03:27,487
No matter how you look at it,
you can't beat him alone!

46
00:03:27,723 --> 00:03:28,621
Leave me be!

47
00:03:28,891 --> 00:03:30,984
This is an important mission for
the Village Hidden in the Sand!

48
00:03:31,660 --> 00:03:33,491
Make Gaara the first priority!

49
00:03:34,697 --> 00:03:38,292
Besides, he's quite my type of a guy...

50
00:03:39,902 --> 00:03:40,994
Go! Kankuro!

51
00:03:43,138 --> 00:03:43,968
I don't think so!

52
00:03:46,609 --> 00:03:47,576
I won't let you get away!

53
00:03:51,413 --> 00:03:52,141
Eat this!

54
00:03:58,921 --> 00:04:00,616
<i>My opponent is that Uchiha kid...</i>

55
00:04:01,223 --> 00:04:04,818
<i>This is not good. I only have</i>
<i>a bit of Chakra left.</i>

56
00:04:08,697 --> 00:04:12,690
<i>I'll stand even less of a chance</i>
<i>if he uses his Sharingan here...</i>

57
00:04:13,435 --> 00:04:17,064
<i>But I need to get him to use</i>
<i>a large amount of Chakra at any cost.</i>

58
00:04:18,374 --> 00:04:21,639
<i>Shall I take care of her in</i>
<i>one hit with Chidori? Or...</i>

59
00:04:22,978 --> 00:04:24,570
<i>In this situation, maybe I should...</i>

60
00:04:38,994 --> 00:04:43,397
<i>As I thought... He's trying to save</i>
<i>some Chakra for Gaara.</i>

61
00:04:45,067 --> 00:04:46,694
Ninja Art: Wind Scythe Jutsu!

62
00:04:58,213 --> 00:04:59,180
Don't underestimate me!

63
00:04:59,415 --> 00:05:00,973
Ninja Art: Sand Storm!

64
00:05:10,893 --> 00:05:14,385
<i>Darn! I have to do something about</i>
<i>that bothersome fan...</i>

65
00:05:15,931 --> 00:05:19,992
<i>Humph... I wonder how long</i>
<i>you'll last with such a way of fighting.</i>

66
00:05:21,370 --> 00:05:22,462
<i>It can't be helped...</i>

67
00:05:27,977 --> 00:05:30,172
<i>It looks like you've finally</i>
<i>gotten serious, eh?</i>

68
00:05:33,415 --> 00:05:35,315
Fire Style: Phoenix. Flower Jutsu!

69
00:05:36,452 --> 00:05:37,942
<i>That's the stuff!</i>

70
00:05:50,866 --> 00:05:52,356
<i>Aim with precision!</i>

71
00:05:53,402 --> 00:05:55,131
Fire Style: Fireball Jutsu!

72
00:05:58,707 --> 00:05:59,605
Did I get her?

73
00:06:02,378 --> 00:06:03,310
Wind Scythe Jutsu!

74
00:06:05,748 --> 00:06:06,806
<i>I've got you.</i>

75
00:06:08,384 --> 00:06:09,043
<i>Oh no!</i>

76
00:06:09,551 --> 00:06:10,142
Now!

77
00:06:14,089 --> 00:06:15,454
You're mine!

78
00:06:22,698 --> 00:06:23,460
Good!

79
00:06:25,901 --> 00:06:28,062
W-What?! Substitution?!

80
00:06:31,707 --> 00:06:32,605
<i>Oh no!</i>

81
00:06:47,423 --> 00:06:51,086
Sorry, but I don't have the time
to be dealing with you forever!

82
00:07:03,806 --> 00:07:08,539
D-Dang it...
G-Gaara, at any cost...

83
00:07:15,517 --> 00:07:16,779
What's that?!

84
00:07:17,352 --> 00:07:19,013
What the heck is going on?

85
00:07:20,956 --> 00:07:23,254
Who the heck is that youth?

86
00:07:25,427 --> 00:07:27,418
Who on earth are you?!

87
00:07:28,764 --> 00:07:32,029
Is it so sudden you can't tell?

88
00:07:32,501 --> 00:07:35,368
It's me. Orochimaru.

89
00:07:37,506 --> 00:07:42,341
It can't be... Have you completed
that Forbidden Jutsu?

90
00:07:48,016 --> 00:07:52,009
I struggled for decades...
after leaving the village.

91
00:07:52,654 --> 00:07:55,680
You're a truly frightening,
inhuman monster!

92
00:08:05,634 --> 00:08:07,625
So, he did it, huh...?

93
00:08:08,704 --> 00:08:11,935
The reason I couldn't select you
to be the Fourth Hokage...

94
00:08:12,875 --> 00:08:15,036
is because of that distorted
consciousness.

95
00:08:59,087 --> 00:09:01,487
I've finally been found out, eh...?

96
00:09:04,826 --> 00:09:05,986
It's too bad.

97
00:09:06,461 --> 00:09:10,488
Orochimaru...
What's the meaning of this?!

98
00:09:10,933 --> 00:09:14,630
Here I'd set that
many booby traps...

99
00:09:16,138 --> 00:09:17,969
so I was quite surprised.

100
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:21,575
But I see... So it was you.

101
00:09:22,211 --> 00:09:25,647
Recently, there has been a steady stream
of people going missing from the village,

102
00:09:25,714 --> 00:09:27,944
from Genin to Chunin,
and even Anbu Black Ops members.

103
00:09:28,517 --> 00:09:32,749
There was also information that
you had been acting strange...

104
00:09:33,689 --> 00:09:34,815
Master Orochimaru...

105
00:09:34,990 --> 00:09:37,288
Why did a Shinobi of your rank
do such a thing?

106
00:09:39,194 --> 00:09:41,185
Shall I kill you, too?

107
00:09:42,998 --> 00:09:46,957
Orochimaru! Sure enough,
this was your doing...?

108
00:09:47,803 --> 00:09:50,533
Say it! What were you doing here?!

109
00:09:50,806 --> 00:09:53,707
Alas! I've been found out.

110
00:09:53,909 --> 00:09:56,469
There's no point in acting cute...

111
00:09:57,980 --> 00:10:01,108
It's for Jutsu development!

112
00:10:01,817 --> 00:10:03,375
Orochi... You!

113
00:10:03,552 --> 00:10:05,349
For that purpose, you did this
to fellow Shinobi?!

114
00:10:06,555 --> 00:10:08,420
As I thought, Forbidden Jutsu, eh...

115
00:10:10,826 --> 00:10:13,294
What is it that you want?

116
00:10:14,096 --> 00:10:15,586
I want everything!

117
00:10:16,498 --> 00:10:18,227
Everything, you say?!

118
00:10:25,507 --> 00:10:31,002
Get every Jutsu and understand
all of the truths of this world!

119
00:10:31,813 --> 00:10:34,714
The one who first mixed
blue and yellow

120
00:10:34,950 --> 00:10:38,750
named the new color made
in that way, green.

121
00:10:39,721 --> 00:10:42,656
I just want to do the same thing.

122
00:10:43,692 --> 00:10:46,024
If blue is Chakra, yellow is a Sign...

123
00:10:46,228 --> 00:10:48,162
and green is a Jutsu.

124
00:10:48,664 --> 00:10:52,100
In the same way that there
are no limits to the kinds of colors,

125
00:10:52,301 --> 00:10:55,828
there are probably also tens
of thousands of Jutsu in this world...

126
00:10:56,471 --> 00:11:00,237
But in order to get any
and all of the Jutsu...

127
00:11:00,309 --> 00:11:05,747
as well as the truths,
a long time is necessary.

128
00:11:06,515 --> 00:11:11,578
It's the one who takes those
long years to know everything,

129
00:11:11,853 --> 00:11:14,913
who can suitably be called
the ultimate individual.

130
00:11:16,958 --> 00:11:20,826
For me, the life span of
the body is too short.

131
00:11:21,363 --> 00:11:22,523
Too fleeting.

132
00:11:24,032 --> 00:11:29,800
Even if I were to be called the Hokage,
if I die, it all ends there.

133
00:11:30,305 --> 00:11:35,038
Orochimaru... Could it be that
the Jutsu you're testing here is...

134
00:11:35,243 --> 00:11:38,076
Right... It sure could be...

135
00:11:47,389 --> 00:11:49,823
Immortality Jutsu!

136
00:11:59,735 --> 00:12:01,396
Immortality Jutsu is a technique of

137
00:12:01,536 --> 00:12:05,666
eternally pooling one's own
spirits into this earth...

138
00:12:05,941 --> 00:12:09,342
In other words,
it's a Revival Jutsu where...

139
00:12:09,911 --> 00:12:15,543
you find a new body, put your own spirit
into that body and take it over.

140
00:12:19,821 --> 00:12:23,348
I assumed my old form until now,

141
00:12:23,625 --> 00:12:28,392
so that you would feel nostalgic
about our reunion...

142
00:12:29,831 --> 00:12:33,130
Aging is an empty thing, isn't it?

143
00:12:33,735 --> 00:12:37,262
I feel that keenly when I look at you.

144
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,831
You'll die here...

145
00:12:41,209 --> 00:12:46,545
and I'll get a younger,
more beautiful and stronger body...

146
00:12:47,382 --> 00:12:51,341
The Leaf truly lets me have my fill of fun...

147
00:12:57,826 --> 00:13:01,227
I get it...
You want Sasuke Uchiha, eh?!

148
00:13:10,939 --> 00:13:15,569
Right... Exactly... Sasuke.

149
00:13:16,644 --> 00:13:18,544
A Reviving Jutsu where
someone else's body is stolen

150
00:13:18,980 --> 00:13:22,040
and the spirit is immortalized, huh?

151
00:13:22,650 --> 00:13:26,416
How many faces and bodies
have you gone through?!

152
00:13:27,722 --> 00:13:30,316
Two, I think...

153
00:13:30,725 --> 00:13:36,061
I plan to take Sasuke over after
raising him a little more to my liking.

154
00:13:40,134 --> 00:13:43,865
But after all, in order to make you regret
your very own life...

155
00:13:43,938 --> 00:13:47,101
and curse destiny as you die...

156
00:13:48,176 --> 00:13:51,441
...perhaps this face is better?

157
00:13:54,249 --> 00:13:55,341
You monster!

158
00:14:07,929 --> 00:14:09,021
Lord Hokage!

159
00:14:14,168 --> 00:14:20,266
Don't lower your guard, Sensei!
You're always too soft...

160
00:14:27,715 --> 00:14:30,513
What's been wrong with you?
This isn't like you!

161
00:14:30,852 --> 00:14:31,978
I'm sorry...

162
00:15:04,986 --> 00:15:05,884
<i>Eyes...</i>

163
00:15:07,055 --> 00:15:09,615
<i>Eyes with malice and ambition</i>
<i>concealed in them...</i>

164
00:15:10,258 --> 00:15:13,318
<i>I had noticed that</i>
<i>you had such tendencies.</i>

165
00:15:14,829 --> 00:15:17,593
<i>I had noticed,</i>
<i>but pretended not to know.</i>

166
00:15:19,133 --> 00:15:21,533
<i>It was still during the war torn era.</i>

167
00:15:21,703 --> 00:15:24,399
<i>A genius who brimmed</i>
<i>over strongly with ability...</i>

168
00:15:24,472 --> 00:15:28,533
<i>Nothing less than a phenomenon</i>
<i>that comes once in several decades.</i>

169
00:15:29,510 --> 00:15:31,774
<i>So I wanted to think that</i>

170
00:15:31,846 --> 00:15:36,044
<i>you would carry on</i>
<i>my own will and power.</i>

171
00:15:37,485 --> 00:15:39,385
<i>That softness on my part...</i>

172
00:15:40,088 --> 00:15:43,854
<i>created the conditions of that time</i>
<i>as well as now!</i>

173
00:15:45,426 --> 00:15:49,226
Are you going to... kill me?

174
00:15:52,066 --> 00:15:53,966
Ninja Art: Summoning jutsu!

175
00:15:58,506 --> 00:16:04,342
I wonder if you can...
Sarutobi Sensei!

176
00:16:22,363 --> 00:16:25,093
Kill him, Sarutobi!
Now's your only chance!

177
00:16:45,386 --> 00:16:47,581
Sarutobi... You...

178
00:16:48,923 --> 00:16:50,982
<i>I couldn't kill him...</i>

179
00:16:53,694 --> 00:16:57,858
I'll bury you and correct
my old mistakes, now!

180
00:17:01,402 --> 00:17:02,369
Here I go!

181
00:17:05,273 --> 00:17:07,571
It's too late!

182
00:17:10,778 --> 00:17:12,905
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

183
00:17:14,549 --> 00:17:16,710
No way!
Why the Shadow Clone Jutsu?!

184
00:17:17,118 --> 00:17:19,586
To disperse the little Chakra
he has left...!

185
00:17:21,322 --> 00:17:23,483
You've gotten old, after all...

186
00:17:24,058 --> 00:17:27,687
To think you'd shorten your
own life span out of impatience...

187
00:17:28,596 --> 00:17:30,086
D-Don't tell me, you?!

188
00:17:32,233 --> 00:17:36,329
Mi, I, Hitsuji, U, Inu, Ne, Tori, Uma, Mi...

189
00:17:38,973 --> 00:17:40,235
<i>This order of Signs...</i>

190
00:17:41,008 --> 00:17:42,999
<i>I knew it, Sarutobi,</i>
<i>you are using that Jutsu!</i>

191
00:17:59,127 --> 00:18:02,858
<i>So this is the Grim Reaper</i>
<i>the Fourth Hokage was talking about,</i>

192
00:18:02,930 --> 00:18:07,299
<i>which only the one who has signed</i>
<i>a contract with this Jutsu can see, eh?!</i>

193
00:18:08,002 --> 00:18:12,336
Whatever you do now, it's too late...
I've won.

194
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:14,703
The Leaf Village will crumble!

195
00:18:15,243 --> 00:18:17,939
The Village Hidden in the Leaves
is the home where I live.

196
00:18:18,246 --> 00:18:24,185
The Hokage exists as the pillar
to protect that home!

197
00:18:24,785 --> 00:18:28,448
The Hokage is the one who inherits
and is entrusted the will of the Leaf.

198
00:18:28,689 --> 00:18:30,680
I won't go easily!

199
00:18:32,660 --> 00:18:34,958
Genjutsu! Infinite Darkness Jutsu!

200
00:18:42,970 --> 00:18:44,597
Stupid nonsense...

201
00:18:45,306 --> 00:18:47,774
You're merely a temporal head

202
00:18:47,842 --> 00:18:51,209
in the history of the organization
called the Leaf Village...

203
00:18:58,653 --> 00:19:03,647
Even the face rock that is left
will eventually weather and decay.

204
00:19:04,792 --> 00:19:09,661
Humph... Leaf Village is
not just an organization to me!

205
00:19:14,068 --> 00:19:15,695
In the Leaf Village,

206
00:19:16,070 --> 00:19:19,301
every year many Shinobi
are born and raised...

207
00:19:19,507 --> 00:19:23,568
and live and fight...
and die to protect the village.

208
00:19:50,037 --> 00:19:52,505
The people of this village...

209
00:19:52,573 --> 00:19:55,167
even if they don't have blood ties...

210
00:19:56,611 --> 00:19:59,409
To me, they are precious...

211
00:20:00,948 --> 00:20:02,176
precious...

212
00:20:03,417 --> 00:20:04,907
family!

213
00:20:13,861 --> 00:20:20,994
Then I shall smash you, the pillar,
and destroy the Leaf home.

214
00:20:21,736 --> 00:20:27,732
Humph! Even if you kill me,
that pillar will not break!

215
00:20:28,576 --> 00:20:34,105
I am the man who carried on the Leaf Will
of the First and Second Hokages...

216
00:20:34,982 --> 00:20:36,472
The Third Hokage!

217
00:20:38,352 --> 00:20:42,516
No matter how much you target
this Village Hidden in the Leaves...

218
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:48,319
A new Hokage will carry on my will,
shall become a pillar and defend the Leaf!

219
00:20:50,064 --> 00:20:51,725
Right, Fourth Hokage?

220
00:20:53,034 --> 00:20:58,438
Orochimaru! Now I will perform
an ace Jutsu that even you don't know!

221
00:20:59,974 --> 00:21:04,206
Behold! Sealing jutsu!
Reaper Death Seal!

222
00:21:05,814 --> 00:21:15,883
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

223
00:21:16,324 --> 00:21:27,167
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

224
00:21:37,278 --> 00:21:42,910
<i>Yes, breathe in the air</i>
<i>Lift your face to the sky and jump</i>

225
00:21:42,984 --> 00:21:47,944
<i>If it rains, take a break</i>
<i>Go where the wind takes you</i>

226
00:21:48,323 --> 00:21:53,226
<i>So many regrets</i>
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>

227
00:21:53,294 --> 00:21:58,425
<i>Let's go carve the badges in our chest</i>
<i>Yes, it's Show Time, life begins now.</i>

228
00:21:58,499 --> 00:22:08,670
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

229
00:22:08,977 --> 00:22:19,410
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

230
00:22:19,487 --> 00:22:30,056
<i>Transform sadness into the wind</i>
<i>and continue to forge on</i>

231
00:22:30,131 --> 00:22:35,694
<i>Forge on strong</i>

232
00:22:47,382 --> 00:22:49,680
Every year in this village

233
00:22:49,751 --> 00:22:53,653
Shinobi are born, nurtured,
and fight for the sake of the village.

234
00:22:53,955 --> 00:22:58,221
They live to protect the village and
things that are precious to them.

235
00:22:58,593 --> 00:23:04,793
Even if they aren't related to me,
they are my precious family.

236
00:23:05,333 --> 00:23:10,930
I won't let you have your way
with my family!

237
00:23:11,439 --> 00:23:14,135
Next time: "Forbidden Secret Technique:
Reaper Death Seal!"
